    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台威胁州和地方政府减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普竞选第二任总统的势头再次引发了人们的担忧，即长期以来的市政债券税收减免可能会被取消，以帮助支付永久性减税的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
