    <item>
      <title>战争持续，泽连斯基“不惧怕”特朗普新总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/zelenskiy-not-afraid-of-new-trump-presidency-as-war-drags-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他“并不害怕”唐纳德·特朗普可能再次担任总统，尽管他表示美国大选的动荡正在损害基辅在战场上的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/zelenskiy-not-afraid-of-new-trump-presidency-as-war-drags-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州法官驳回特朗普机密文件案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissed-by-florida-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国法官驳回了对唐纳德·特朗普不当处理机密信息的刑事指控，这一事件的发生距美国联邦调查局特工搜查特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园以寻找丢失的国家机密以及特朗普努力重回白宫约两年后发生了非同寻常的转折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-classified-documents-case-dismissed-by-florida-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:55:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场在反弹后“特朗普交易”增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遇刺未遂之后，世界金融市场重新开放，有一件事很明显：特朗普交易正在获得动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后乐观情绪推动加密货币价格上涨，比特币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对暗杀企图作出坚决回应，引发人们猜测这位支持加密货币的前总统赢得连任的机会有所增加，随后比特币出现了近两个月来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
